

=Bio=

"Sound Engineer, Executive Producer (Cultural area), researcher in communications. Latin Grammy awarded in 2006 for the recording work with the album "Hoje" from the brazilian rock band Paralamas do Sucesso. Latin Grammy nominee with the recording work with argentine folcloric chanteuse Mercedes Sosa. Production of educational and artistic projects such as "Projeto Elos" (infos at www.projetoelos.com.br) and "Marco Universal II" (infos at www.marcouniversal.com.br) Masters course in Communication at the Federal University of Rio de Janeiro (UFRJ) to be concluded in 2013. Research line: Communication's technologies and aesthetics. Graduate (baccalaureate) in Cultural Production at the Fluminense Federal University (UFF).

Let's go to what matters: Home-brewer and P2P culture enthusiast. :) "


